00:00:03.272 --> 00:00:07.433
Namaskar! Welcome to nishamadhulika.com

00:00:07.756 --> 00:00:13.026
Today we are going to make the kheer of flattened rice.

00:00:13.383 --> 00:00:15.758
This kheer is made easily.

00:00:16.078 --> 00:00:20.545
This kheer is as delicious as the kheer made using normal rice.

00:00:21.399 --> 00:00:24.553
So come, let's prepare flattened rice kheer.

00:00:24.812 --> 00:00:36.659
Flattened (Chivda/Poha) rice - 1/2 cup (35 gms)

00:00:36.971 --> 00:00:40.799
Sugar - 1/4 Cup (60 gms)

00:00:40.899 --> 00:00:42.933
Cashew nuts - 1 tbsp

00:00:43.133 --> 00:00:45.115
Raisins - 1 tbsp

00:00:45.403 --> 00:00:47.119
Pistachios - 12 to 15

00:00:47.319 --> 00:00:49.318
Green cardamom - 4

00:00:49.618 --> 00:00:55.840
Full cream milk - 500 ml

00:00:56.122 --> 00:00:58.962
Firstly, let us boil the milk.

00:00:59.433 --> 00:01:07.856
Till then let us cut the cashews, pistachios and make a powder of cardamom.

00:01:08.351 --> 00:01:13.247
Cut 1 cashew nut into 6- 7 pieces each.

00:01:17.208 --> 00:01:23.067
Cut the pistachios into thin slices.

00:01:25.665 --> 00:01:31.782
Once the milk is boiled, add flattened rice to it.

00:01:32.435 --> 00:01:45.390
Cook it on medium flame till it is thoroughly cooked.

00:01:45.690 --> 00:01:51.942
Keep stirring after every 2-3 minutes.

00:01:52.405 --> 00:01:58.316
Now add the cashews, raisins and pistachios to the kheer.

00:01:58.540 --> 00:02:02.645
Leave a few pistachios for the end to garnish the kheer.

00:02:06.796 --> 00:02:16.641
In place of cashews, pistachios you can also add almonds or chironji.

00:02:16.965 --> 00:02:21.606
You can add dry fruits as per your choice and availability.

00:02:22.175 --> 00:02:25.277
Our flattened rice kheer is now cooked.

00:02:25.595 --> 00:02:37.880
Check this way and make sure the milk and flattened rice are thoroughly mixed.

00:02:38.352 --> 00:02:40.088
Add sugar to it.

00:02:40.661 --> 00:02:45.066
Keep stirring for 1-2 minutes so that the sugar is dissolved in the kheer.

00:02:46.011 --> 00:02:50.511
You can increase the quantity of sugar as per your taste.

00:02:51.347 --> 00:02:54.660
Add cardamom powder as well.

00:02:56.361 --> 00:03:06.966
It ttook us 15 minutes to prepare the kheer.

00:03:07.534 --> 00:03:09.255
take out the kheer in a bowl.

00:03:13.236 --> 00:03:17.369
Garnish the kheer with pistachios.

00:03:18.839 --> 00:03:26.203
Flattened rice is now ready. this kheer is delicious.

00:03:26.203 --> 00:03:39.710
Whenever you feel like eating something you can try out this kheer, as it is easily prepared.

00:03:40.002 --> 00:03:44.681
This quantity is sufficient for 2-3 members of the family.

